original_title: Poncho Sanchez: A Night at Kimball's East
overview: Grammy Award-winning Latin jazz percussionist Poncho Sanchez performs some of his biggest hits (going back a quarter of a century) before a live audience at the venerable jazz venue Kimball's East. Songs include "Alafia," "Jumpin' with Symphony Sid," "Co Co May May," "Cinderella," "Half and Half" and "Baila Mi Gene."
title: Poncho Sanchez: A Night at Kimball's East
